/* mix in the jsdoc-parse and dmd options */
let definitions = jsdocDefinitions
  .map(def => {
    def.group = 'jsdoc'
    return def
  })
  .concat(jsdoc2mdDefinitions.map(def => {
    def.group = 'jsdoc2md'
    return def
  }))
  .concat(dmdDefinitions.map(function (def) {
    def.group = 'dmd'
    return def
  }))
 
module.exports = {
  definitions: definitions,
  usageSections: [
